 quickly . ^ i only make these  um points because they relate to the geological record , and the age of the earth ; there are many other personal problems i could raise with evolutionary theory , but that is for another day . ^  ame </text_embedded><text_normal> ^  ame  ame  ame ^ st.  ame 's college ^  um  ame  ame  ame  ame  ame ^ department of geological sciences university of  ame ^ mobile ( vodafone )  um  um  um  um </text_normal></message_body></message>